summary: This is an email transmitting the public portion of a court hearing transcript from the case US v Maxwell (20-cr-330). It indicates a sealed portion exists and will be sent separately. The document serves as a cover note for the attached transcript.

events.title: Hearing in US v Maxwell
events.description: A court hearing was held in the case US v Maxwell, 20-cr-330. A transcript was produced, with portions designated as public and sealed.

keyFacts: A hearing was held on November 10, 2021, in the criminal case US v Maxwell (docket 20-cr-330).
A transcript of the hearing was produced, with a public portion and a sealed portion.
The sealed portion of the transcript was to be handled via separate email transmission.
The document is a cover email for the attached public transcript file (LBAAMAXH.pdf).
